Okay.

263
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:56,960
In this case,

264
00:17:57,759 --> 00:18:00,680
as you are the second shopkeeper
of Huamanzhu, I must give you the money.

265
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:02,759
Keep it close for your use.

266
00:18:02,759 --> 00:18:05,640
Mudan, you've already done enough for me.

267
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:07,319
There's no need to say these things between us.

268
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,440
For Huamanzhu's success today,

269
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,920
I am aware of all your contributions.

270
00:18:16,279 --> 00:18:18,079
Keep this money well.

271
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:21,079
Make sure Wang Qing doesn't find it out.

272
00:18:28,359 --> 00:18:29,799
There is another item.

273
00:18:29,799 --> 00:18:33,519
I intended to keep it to give to you
when there's a chance in the future.

274
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:37,920
In this case, I will bring it too.

275
00:18:45,559 --> 00:18:46,624
Shengyi,

276
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:49,888
wait for me.

277
00:19:01,119 --> 00:19:02,519
Shengyi.

278
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,400
Shengyi.

279
00:19:07,519 --> 00:19:08,800
Shengyi.

280
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:15,119
This name really sounds nice.

281
00:19:31,955 --> 00:19:35,392
<i>[Huamanzhu]</i>

282
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,072
Thank you, everyone.

283
00:19:40,039 --> 00:19:41,319
Although our Huamanzhu

284
00:19:41,319 --> 00:19:44,440
made a name at the birthday banquet
in the Tang Mansion,

285
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:46,680
noblemen are still rare.

286
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:48,920
It's the common people
who are in the big world.

287
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,720
In the future, our business

288
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:53,920
will still rely on individual flowers
and boxes of incense powder.

289
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:56,599
Don't entertain thoughts
of deceit and trickery.

290
00:19:56,599 --> 00:19:57,600
Understood.

291
00:19:58,240 --> 00:20:01,599
The jasmine, gardenia, and wild roses
we improved before

292
00:20:01,599 --> 00:20:04,119
have a long bloom period and robust flowers.

293
00:20:04,119 --> 00:20:06,119
They can be used as affordable potted plants.

294
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:07,880
As for the expensive ones,

295
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:10,559
cymbidiums, roses, and lotuses,

296
00:20:11,279 --> 00:20:14,240
be sure to explain clearly
to the customers before selling

297
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:16,519
that they have a short bloom time
and are difficult to care for.

298
00:20:16,519 --> 00:20:18,240
But their value lies in their rarity.

299
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:19,960
Only Huamanzhu can cultivate them.

300
00:20:20,599 --> 00:20:22,519
If the customers have any doubts,

301
00:20:22,519 --> 00:20:24,119
we must not, for the sake of selling flowers,

302
00:20:24,119 --> 00:20:26,200
lie or deceive people, understood?

303
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,264
Understood.

304
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,759
People who are willing
to spend money on these flowers

305
00:20:29,759 --> 00:20:31,079
want something different from others.

306
00:20:31,079 --> 00:20:33,480
Most of them don't care
about the length of the bloom period.

307
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:34,560
You're right.

308
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:37,480
Mudan, I've used our new summer flowers

309
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:38,720
to mix a few new kinds of incense powder.

310
00:20:39,319 --> 00:20:41,119
Come and try the scent later.

311
00:20:41,119 --> 00:20:44,000
Okay, we can then come up
with more elegant names for them.

312
00:20:44,599 --> 00:20:47,079
Madam, I think the flowers used in the sachets

313
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:48,279
can be changed accordingly.

314
00:20:48,279 --> 00:20:49,440
What do you think?

315
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:50,528
I'll go with your suggestion.

316
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:56,519
Tomorrow, I'll go to your place to see

317
00:20:56,519 --> 00:20:58,279
the newly cultivated Thousand-Petal Lotus.

318
00:20:58,279 --> 00:21:01,039
This flower attracts insects
more easily than other lotuses.

319
00:21:01,039 --> 00:21:02,440
If I am not around,

320
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:04,480
I hope you two will be extra careful.

321
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:07,200
We conduct regular patrols at night.

322
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:09,519
We will never let such precious flowers
be harmed by insects.

323
00:21:10,079 --> 00:21:11,200
Thank you for your efforts.

324
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:28,200
I suddenly met with a misfortune before.

325
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:31,400
I have yet to settle the monthly payments
for everyone.

326
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,559
But you bear no grudges

327
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:36,319
and still wish to do business with me.

328
00:21:37,119 --> 00:21:38,144
I'm very grateful.

329
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:42,079
I hope that in the future, everyone can
work together with me with one heart.

330
00:21:42,599 --> 00:21:44,240
Once I open a new store,

331
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:47,799
I will increase everyone's monthly earnings
by twenty percent, is that okay?

332
00:21:47,799 --> 00:21:50,559
Good, thank you, Miss.

333
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:53,000
You're kind and trustworthy.

334
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:55,400
We have no worries
about food and clothing following you.

335
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,960
Naturally, we will be fully dedicated.

336
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,119
Please be assured.

337
00:22:00,519 --> 00:22:01,559
Thank you all for your hard work.

338
00:22:05,319 --> 00:22:07,200
Put some effort into it, grind it fine.

339
00:22:07,799 --> 00:22:08,960
Okay.

340
00:22:12,359 --> 00:22:13,400
Pat it.

341
00:22:15,279 --> 00:22:16,359
Gently sift it in a circular motion.

342
00:22:18,208 --> 00:22:20,992
