343
00:22:20,992 --> 00:22:26,304
<i>♫ The shadow of youth is ever-present ♫</i>

344
00:22:26,304 --> 00:22:29,184
<i>♫ Still cherish the moon of my hometown ♫</i>

345
00:22:29,184 --> 00:22:34,440
<i>♫ To meet for long ♫</i>

346
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:37,359
Mother, it won't be long,

347
00:22:38,279 --> 00:22:39,920
I will definitely take back
our Fragrance Garden.

348
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,440
Just wait and see.

349
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:54,839
Every time Mr. Liu takes the horse for a walk,

350
00:22:54,839 --> 00:22:57,160
Your Highness would come
to this desolate place to watch him.

351
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:59,880
However, he does not say a word.

352
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:02,880
Why should Your Highness of noble birth
suffer such grievances?

353
00:23:03,799 --> 00:23:05,400
Zishu is proud by heart.

354
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:06,960
He was demoted to the Stables Bureau.

355
00:23:07,799 --> 00:23:10,000
It was my father
who forced him to face reality.

356
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:13,160
He acts this way because he harbors
resentment in his heart.

357
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,304
I don't blame him.

358
00:23:14,839 --> 00:23:17,480
It's just that Zishu will one day understand

359
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:19,960
