00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:07,160
County Princess Ji'an is in danger.
Come quickly to rescue!

392
00:25:07,759 --> 00:25:09,039
Help!

393
00:25:10,119 --> 00:25:11,880
Your Highness, what should we do?

394
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:13,568
It's getting darker.

395
00:25:13,568 --> 00:25:14,799
If we still…

396
00:25:14,799 --> 00:25:16,079
What's the use of crying?

397
00:25:16,079 --> 00:25:17,359
If you don't want to die here, keep shouting.

