438
00:27:51,519 --> 00:27:53,039
She wrongfully died tragically in the army.

439
00:27:54,559 --> 00:27:55,616
Apart from me,

440
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:59,240
who else would remember her?

441
00:28:02,119 --> 00:28:03,279
Your Highness!

442
00:28:04,119 --> 00:28:05,440
Your Highness!

443
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,599
Your Highness!

444
00:28:07,359 --> 00:28:10,920
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

445
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,456
Go fetch the paper kite.

446
00:28:47,456 --> 00:28:48,512
Yes.

447
00:29:02,599 --> 00:29:04,559
It was the birthday of the Eastern Capital's
caretaker a few days ago.

448
00:29:04,559 --> 00:29:07,240
Liu Shen didn't go but sent two large boxes
of congratulatory gifts.

449
00:29:07,240 --> 00:29:09,519
The gifts are so valuable,
far exceeding his annual salary.

450
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:13,160
When entertaining in Luoyang,

451
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,799
he was using the daughter-in-law's dowry
to supplement.

452
00:29:15,519 --> 00:29:17,279
How long has it been
since he came to in Chang'an?

453
00:29:17,279 --> 00:29:18,559
