454
00:29:19,559 --> 00:29:22,160
Truly a big rat eating my millet.

455
00:29:22,799 --> 00:29:23,799
Liu Chang was demoted,

456
00:29:24,319 --> 00:29:26,720
but his father's position as the Minister
of the Imperial Treasury is so securely held.

457
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:27,839
It must be with the tacit consent
of Prince Ning.

458
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:33,119
We must find out
where Liu Shen's money comes from.

459
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:36,799
How to start bringing down Mr. Chen

460
00:29:36,799 --> 00:29:38,848
depends on whether the Liu family
is impenetrable.

461
00:29:38,848 --> 00:29:39,960
Yes.

462
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,440
Lady He, you've come.

463
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:42,519
Is Mr. Jiang here?

464
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:45,960
Mr. Jiang has instructed, he is currently…

465
00:29:50,839 --> 00:29:52,079
Mr. Jiang, this is…

466
00:29:56,079 --> 00:29:57,880
A new slingshot prepared for the children.

467
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,839
Just right to test if it can be pulled.

468
00:30:16,759 --> 00:30:19,000
You plant flowers on ordinary days,
so your hands are indeed strong.

469
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:20,960
It's just the aim is too poor.

470
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:24,000
Do you have poor eyesight?

471
00:30:25,359 --> 00:30:26,680
Among thousands of people,

472
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:28,880
I spotted your extraordinariness
at first glance.

473
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,119
Is my eyesight not good?

474
00:30:32,039 --> 00:30:33,559
