475
00:30:34,519 --> 00:30:37,440
If I practice, I might not miss.

476
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:43,880
Rather than picking a date,
it's better to just make it happen.

477
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:46,720
Let's practice today.

