00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:55,328
Zhaocai.

479
00:31:05,839 --> 00:31:06,880
My lord, spare my life.

480
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:19,480
You are not usually one
to torment your servants.

481
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,640
What's the matter today?

482
00:31:21,319 --> 00:31:23,160
My aim is poor.

483
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,359
How is it torment?

484
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:27,680
You know it in your heart

485
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:29,200
