486
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,000
But he doesn't know that.

487
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,799
He must be feeling frightened.

488
00:31:33,799 --> 00:31:36,440
If you can't bear to watch, let it be.

489
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:45,720
Mr. Jiang, I've just recently
gotten back Huamanzhu.

490
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:47,552
The interest for this month isn't that much.

491
00:31:47,552 --> 00:31:48,680
Please be patient with me.

492
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:50,400
Rest assured, next month,

493
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,720
I definitely won't disappoint you.

494
00:31:52,359 --> 00:31:55,519
Also, the money for the previous purchasing
from my hometown is all in there.

495
00:31:57,559 --> 00:32:00,000
Besides…

496
00:32:00,799 --> 00:32:02,079
I want to retrieve my own indenture.

497
00:32:02,079 --> 00:32:03,880
I want to drink wine and chat with Mudan.

498
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:06,720
You go fly this paper kite.

499
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,319
Fly it higher.

500
00:32:08,319 --> 00:32:11,079
If you can win a smile from Mudan,
there will be a reward.

501
00:32:11,799 --> 00:32:12,864
Yes.

502
00:32:21,599 --> 00:32:24,720
What are you flying there? Go down and fly it.

503
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,856
Yes.

504
00:32:41,319 --> 00:32:43,519
Do you have a grudge against this lad?

505
00:32:45,799 --> 00:32:46,839
You guess.

506
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,664
Chuanyu.

507
00:32:59,799 --> 00:33:03,039
Mr. Jiang, the money with which you bought me,

508
00:33:03,039 --> 00:33:04,279
I've also put it in there.

509
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:06,112
It's placed here.

510
00:33:08,680 --> 00:33:11,279
Mr. Jiang, when you're free,

511
00:33:11,279 --> 00:33:12,640
could you go to the authorities

512
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:16,559
to change my household registration?

513
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:20,319
I understand, the favor of getting
a decent register is another matter.

514
00:33:20,319 --> 00:33:22,880
You name a price, I will definitely
make up the amount next time.

515
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:26,039
You previously said we were good friends.

516
00:33:26,039 --> 00:33:27,400
Today you're acting so distant.

517
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,799
It's not the first time dealing with documents
for a decent household register.

518
00:33:29,799 --> 00:33:30,960
I'm not short of this bit of money.

519
00:33:31,759 --> 00:33:34,880
Yes, it's just that even brothers
must settle accounts clearly.

520
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:38,200
With give and take, only then
can a friendship last long.

521
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:41,240
Moreover, a big favor
like getting a decent register,

522
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:44,759
