558
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:24,199
there's nothing we can do.

559
00:35:24,199 --> 00:35:25,760
We did what we could.

560
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:27,119
As long as our conscience is clear.

561
00:35:28,199 --> 00:35:30,360
