about what they had eaten.

568
00:35:52,199 --> 00:35:54,280
It seems there was nothing abnormal.

569
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,599
Thinking about it, ordinary people

570
00:35:56,599 --> 00:35:57,840
mostly eat corn as their staple.

571
00:35:58,360 --> 00:36:00,679
They naturally feel there is nothing wrong
with food they are accustomed to eating

572
00:36:00,679 --> 00:36:01,960
and wouldn't specifically report it.

573
00:36:02,679 --> 00:36:05,760
Could this be why I've never been able
to find the cause of the illness?

574
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:08,760
I'll go with you to confirm it.

575
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:11,000
See if those people ate corn
from the same source.

576
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,039
Fu, stop scratching.

577
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:14,976
It's itchy.

578
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,320
Sesame seed cakes.

579
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,719
Make way, please.

580
00:36:23,719 --> 00:36:24,800
Make way, please.

581
00:36:27,104 --> 00:36:28,159
Make way, please.

582
00:36:28,159 --> 00:36:29,480
Sheep liver cakes.

583
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:33,719
The rice and wheat vendors at the West Market

584
00:36:33,719 --> 00:36:35,280
have actually adulterated
the grain with moldy corn.

585
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:38,840
Eating such moldy corn every day

586
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:40,360
will cause serious health issues.

587
00:36:41,079 --> 00:36:42,639
Who on earth is committing this atrocity?

588
00:36:45,152 --> 00:36:46,176
How is it?

589
00:36:47,239 --> 00:36:48,360
The rice from the East Market is fine.

590
00:36:54,079 --> 00:36:55,679
The rice from the East Market is fine.

591
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:58,400
The East Market is frequented by the nobility

592
00:36:58,960 --> 00:37:01,119
while the West Market is
our common people's marketplace.

593
00:37:02,599 --> 00:37:05,480
I didn't expect them
to be profiteering like this.

594
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,512
Who are they?

595
00:37:12,159 --> 00:37:13,184
We must act quickly.

596
00:37:14,079 --> 00:37:15,168
Okay, Master Liu.

597
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:16,960
Master Liu, take care.

598
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:28,119
I previously hired someone at the black market
to follow Liu Shen continuously.

599
00:37:28,119 --> 00:37:31,400
Liu Shen is very close to the market official
who oversees both the East and West Markets.

600
00:37:32,280 --> 00:37:33,760
This market official has held his position
for many years

601
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:35,360
and has never made a mistake.

602
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:37,079
Therefore, I did not pay attention
to it previously

603
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:41,599
until I discovered the moldy corn.

604
00:37:41,599 --> 00:37:43,400
I sent someone to investigate carefully.

605
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:47,480
Indeed, since Liu Shen became
the superior of this person,

606
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,840
not just rice and wheat,

607
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:52,320
